result.name: Fook Lam Moon (Kowloon) Restaurant

reviews.text: Amazing food and the quality is so good.

Refined dim sum experience with a large menu to supplement your experience.  We splurged and had the double boiled soup of the day - fish, pork, herbs and vegetables which was very tasty (c. US$40) and sampled the typical dim sum plates which were prepared very well.  The pan fried noodles were also perfectly done.  Cost here is a little higher than average but worth it and service is punctual and attentive.
Good food. But Too expensive. More than double price than other Restaurants. 너무 비싸네요
Food is ok, service is bad
Could not fault this place at all. Perfect dim sum meal to end our trip. Char siew pao and siew mai we're heavenly. A bit more $$ than normal, but we'll worth it.

reviews.text:
沒吃過1200台幣的炒飯，真的厲害!
但服務態度以台灣人標準還是有待加強

お昼に飲茶をしに訪れました。地元の方おすすめのお店。
どの料理も優しい味でいくらでも食べられます。
優質中菜，價錢也高級！
無論生客熟客都當熟客咁做，招呼一流，荷葉飯獨步全港。
飲茶 少しずつ 楽しめました！細麺のかた焼きそばが優しいお味で 最高に美味でした！日本ではなかなか会えないお味✨
